// WorkspacePanel
// Simple two-section vertical layout: chat message area on top (flex 1) and
// embedded terminal on bottom (flex 2).

FUNCTION WorkspacePanel(messageContent) -> JSX                         EXPORT
  CALLS: EmbeddedTerminal (EmbeddedTerminal)
  Renders messageContent in the top div and EmbeddedTerminal in the bottom div.
  No local state or logic.
